{"id":29,"parent_id":4,"book_id":4,"content_id":1,"language_id":1,"display_order":29,"title":"D&C 25","subtitle":"","short_title":"D&C","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/25","content":[["div",[".titleNumber","Section 25"],[".studyIntro",["i","Revelation given through Joseph Smith the Prophet, at Harmony, Pennsylvania, July 1830 (see the",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/24.head"},"heading to section 24"],"). This revelation manifests the will of the Lord to Emma Smith, the Prophet’s wife."]],[".studySummary",["i",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/25.1-6"},"1–6"],", Emma Smith, an elect lady, is called to aid and comfort her husband;",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/25.7-11"},"7–11"],", She is also called to write, to expound scriptures, and to select hymns;",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/25.12-14"},"12–14"],", The song of the righteous is a prayer unto the Lord;",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/25.15-16"},"15–16"],", Principles of obedience in this revelation are applicable to all."]]],[".bodyBlock",["div",{"id":"1","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/25.1","order":"06.05.025.3103"},["b","1"],"Hearken unto the voice of the Lord your God, while I speak unto you, Emma Smith, my daughter; for verily I say unto you, all those who",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_1a"},"receive"],"my gospel are sons and daughters in my",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_1b"},"kingdom"],"."],["div",{"id":"2","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/25.2","order":"06.05.025.3104"},["b","2"],"A revelation I give unto you concerning my will; and if thou art faithful and",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_2a"},"walk"],"in the paths of",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_2b"},"virtue"],"before me, I will preserve thy life, and thou shalt receive an",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_2c"},"inheritance"],"in Zion."],["div",{"id":"3","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/25.3","order":"06.05.025.3105"},["b","3"],"Behold, thy",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_3a"},"sins"],"are forgiven thee, and thou art an",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_3b"},"elect"],["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_3c"},"lady"],", whom I have",["sup","d"],["a",{"href":"fn_3d"},"called"],"."],["div",{"id":"4","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/25.4","order":"06.05.025.3106"},["b","4"],["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_4a"},"Murmur"],"not because of the",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_4b"},"things"],"which thou hast not seen, for they are",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_4c"},"withheld"],"from thee and from the world, which is wisdom in me in a time to come."],["div",{"id":"5","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/25.5","order":"06.05.025.3107"},["b","5"],"And the office of thy calling shall be for a",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_5a"},"comfort"],"unto my servant, Joseph Smith, Jun., thy",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_5b"},"husband"],", in his",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_5c"},"afflictions"],", with consoling words, in the spirit of",["sup","d"],["a",{"href":"fn_5d"},"meekness"],"."],["div",{"id":"6","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/25.6","order":"06.05.025.3108"},["b","6"],"And thou shalt go with him at the time of his going, and be unto him for a scribe, while there is no one to be a scribe for him, that I may send my servant, Oliver Cowdery, whithersoever I will."],["div",{"id":"7","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/25.7","order":"06.05.025.3109"},["b","7"],"And thou shalt be",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_7a"},"ordained"],"under his hand to expound scriptures, and to exhort the church, according as it shall be given thee by my",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_7b"},"Spirit"],"."],["div",{"id":"8","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/25.8","order":"06.05.025.3110"},["b","8"],"For he shall lay his",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_8a"},"hands"],"upon thee, and thou shalt receive the Holy Ghost, and thy time shall be given to writing, and to learning much."],["div",{"id":"9","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/25.9","order":"06.05.025.3111"},["b","9"],"And thou needest not fear, for thy",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_9a"},"husband"],"shall support thee in the church; for unto them is his",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_9b"},"calling"],", that all things might be",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_9c"},"revealed"],"unto them, whatsoever I will, according to their faith."],["div",{"id":"10","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/25.10","order":"06.05.025.3112"},["b","10"],"And verily I say unto thee that thou shalt lay aside the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_10a"},"things"],"of this",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_10b"},"world"],", and",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_10c"},"seek"],"for the things of a",["sup","d"],["a",{"href":"fn_10d"},"better"],"."],["div",{"id":"11","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/25.11","order":"06.05.025.3113"},["b","11"],"And it shall be given thee, also, to make a selection of",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_11a"},"sacred"],["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_11b"},"hymns"],", as it shall be given thee, which is pleasing unto me, to be had in my church."],["div",{"id":"12","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/25.12","order":"06.05.025.3114"},["b","12"],"For my soul",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_12a"},"delighteth"],"in the",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_12b"},"song"],"of the",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_12c"},"heart"],"; yea, the",["sup","d"],["a",{"href":"fn_12d"},"song"],"of the righteous is a prayer unto me, and it shall be answered with a blessing upon their heads."],["div",{"id":"13","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/25.13","order":"06.05.025.3115"},["b","13"],"Wherefore,",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_13a"},"lift up"],"thy heart and",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_13b"},"rejoice"],", and cleave unto the covenants which thou hast made."],["div",{"id":"14","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/25.14","order":"06.05.025.3116"},["b","14"],"Continue in the spirit of meekness, and beware of",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_14a"},"pride"],". Let thy soul delight in thy",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_14b"},"husband"],", and the",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_14c"},"glory"],"which shall come upon him."],["div",{"id":"15","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/25.15","order":"06.05.025.3117"},["b","15"],"Keep my commandments continually, and a",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_15a"},"crown"],"of",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_15b"},"righteousness"],"thou shalt receive. And except thou do this, where I am you",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_15c"},"cannot"],"come."],["div",{"id":"16","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/25.16","order":"06.05.025.3118"},["b","16"],"And verily, verily, I say unto you, that this is my",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_16a"},"voice"],"unto all. Amen."]]],"refs":[["div",{"id":"1a","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/25.1a","order":"06.05.025.3119"},["b","1a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/john/1.12"},"John 1:12"],".",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/sons-and-daughters-of-god"},"TG Sons and Daughters of God"],"."],["div",{"id":"1b","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/25.1b","order":"06.05.025.3121"},["b","1b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/kingdom-of-god-on-earth"},"TG Kingdom of God, on Earth"],"."],["div",{"id":"2a","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/25.2a","order":"06.05.025.3123"},["b","2a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/deut/30.16"},"Deut. 30:16"],"."],["div",{"id":"2b","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/25.2b","order":"06.05.025.3125"},["b","2b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/virtue"},"TG Virtue"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/zion"},"Zion"],"."],["div",{"id":"2c","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/25.2c","order":"06.05.025.3127"},["b","2c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/52.42.2,5,42"},"D&C 52:42 (2, 5, 42)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/58.51.17,28,51"},"58:51 (17, 28, 51)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/63.48.29,31,48"},"63:48 (29, 31, 48)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/64.30"},"64:30"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/85.7.1-3,7,9"},"85:7 (1–3, 7, 9)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/99.7"},"99:7"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/101.18.1,6,18"},"101:18 (1, 6, 18)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/103.14.11,14"},"103:14 (11, 14)"],"."],["div",{"id":"3a","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/25.3a","order":"06.05.025.3129"},["b","3a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/matt/9.2"},"Matt. 9:2"],"."],["div",{"id":"3b","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/25.3b","order":"06.05.025.3131"},["b","3b"],["span.small","IE"],"one chosen or set apart.",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/2-jn/1.1.1,13"},"2 Jn. 1:1 (1, 13)"],"."],["div",{"id":"3c","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/25.3c","order":"06.05.025.3133"},["b","3c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/woman"},"TG Woman"],"."],["div",{"id":"3d","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/25.3d","order":"06.05.025.3135"},["b","3d"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/authority"},"TG Authority"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/called-of-god"},"Called of God"],"."],["div",{"id":"4a","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/25.4a","order":"06.05.025.3137"},["b","4a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/murmuring"},"TG Murmuring"],"."],["div",{"id":"4b","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/25.4b","order":"06.05.025.3139"},["b","4b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/knowledge"},"TG Knowledge"],"."],["div",{"id":"4c","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/25.4c","order":"06.05.025.3141"},["b","4c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/luke/24.16.10-24"},"Luke 24:16 (10–24)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/40.3"},"Alma 40:3"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/ether/3.25"},"Ether 3:25"],".",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/god-wisdom-of"},"TG God, Wisdom of"],"."],["div",{"id":"5a","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/25.5a","ord